ght test files contain mock implementations or test calls to ScoreExtensions():\n1. **pkg/scheduler/framework/runtime/framework_test.go** - TestScoreWithNormalizePlugin, TestScorePlugin, TestPlugin\n2. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/interpodaffinity/scoring_test.go** - tests calling ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()\n3. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/nodeaffinity/node_affinity_test.go** - tests calling ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()\n4. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/tainttoleration/taint_toleration_test.go** - tests calling ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()\n5. **pkg/scheduler/schedule_one_test.go** - falseMapPlugin, numericMapPlugin, reverseNumericMapPlugin, trueMapPlugin\n6. **test/integration/scheduler/plugins/plugins_test.go** - ScorePlugin, ScoreWithNormalizePlugin\n7. **pkg/scheduler/testing/framework/fake_extender.go** - node2PrioritizerPlugin\n8. **pkg/scheduler/testing/framework/fake_plugins.go** - FakePreScoreAndScorePlugin\n\nThe migration requires updating the interface definition, all eight plugin implementations, the runtime framework call site, metrics constant naming, and all eight test files for a total of 19 files across the kubernetes--v1.32.0 repository."
